# Code Owners for OpenCode Machina
#
# This file defines who owns specific files/directories and requires their review
# for changes. Lines starting with # are comments.
#
# Format:
#   path/to/file @owner1 @owner2
#   path/to/directory/ @owner
#
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Global maintainers - review all PRs by default
# Update these usernames when maintainers are added
# * @maintainer1 @maintainer2

# Release governance - requires review for RELEASE.md changes
# RELEASE.md @release-maintainer

# Security files - requires security team review
# SECURITY.md @security-team

# Core packages - requires maintainer review
# packages/ @maintainer

# Configuration files - requires maintainer review
# .github/ @maintainer
# tsconfig.json @maintainer
# package.json @maintainer
